data.description: Welcome to your new haven of comfort and style! Nestled in the heart of Upland, this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers a warm and welcoming atmosphere, perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. Step into the recently updated interior, adorned with fresh paint and new carpeting,  presenting a modern and revitalized aesthetic. The spacious living room boasts soaring ceilings, creating an open and airy feel, while a charming fireplace adds a touch of homeliness and warmth to the space. Experience the joy of outdoor living with the enclosed patio—a tranquil retreat for unwinding or hosting gatherings. The convenience of an attached 2-car garage and driveway ensures ample parking and storage space, making daily life a breeze.  Positioned strategically behind a sprawling green park, this residence provides not only a serene backdrop but also easy access to outdoor activities. Embrace the lifestyle this prime location offers, with close proximity to freeways and a variety of stores for your convenience.  Imagine the possibilities as you envision transforming this property into your dream home. With a touch of creativity, this residence has the potential to become a personalized sanctuary.
